<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
<head>
<style type="text/css">
[lang|=en]
{
color:red;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<h1>可以应用样式：</h1>
<p lang="en">Hello!</p>
<p lang="en-us">Hi!</p>
<hr />

<h1>无法应用样式：</h1>
<p lang="us">Hi!</p>
<p lang="zh">Hao!</p>
</body>
</html>